Grid
    -Normal div takes up the 100% width of the parent div.
    -Grid allows us to display the elements in grid like fashion.
Row and Col
    -Has 12 grids
offset
    -Adjust remaining width(sizes) of the screen.
Vertical alignment
    -Aligns the text vertically at the center of the div.


    Hide/Show elements

    .Hide                     -         Hidden for all Devices
    .hide-on-small-only       -         Hidden for Mobile Only
    .hide-on-med-only         -         Hidden for Tablet Only
    .hide-on-med-and-down     -         Hidden for tablet and below
    .hide-on-med-and-up       -         Hidden for tablet and Above
    .hide-on-med-large-only   -         Hidden for desktop only
    .show-on-small            -         Show for Mobile Only
    .show-on-medium           -         Show for Tablet Only
    .show-on-large            -         Show for Desktop Only
    .show-on-medium-and-up    -         Show for Tablet and above
    .show-on-medium-and-down  -         Show for Tablet and below

hoverable
    -Applies shadow effects on hoverable

Responsive Image
    -Adjust the sizes automatically to its device screen.


Circular Image
    -Image in circle shape.(Elipse shape for rectange)
    -Perfect circle shape on square images.

Buttons
    -Can be implemented using "btn" class
    Properties:
    btn-small : Reduced the padding
    btn-large : Increases the padding
    Effects
    Waves-effect -> generate waves on clicking the button.
    waves-light  -> light waves on clicking the button.
    waves-colors -> waves color on clicking the button.(E.g. red,green, yellow..)

